# Prod / split stack (PC-5): runbooks and references stay in `docs/` and `docs/TASK_CHECKLIST.md`. Do not add a
# “two-file deploy / production split” section to the root `README.md` — that stack is out of band for
# default project docs. Ignore only local or machine-specific prod-env scratch files (not `*.md` runbooks in git).
.env.prod.local
*.prod.local.md
